#. module: team_sports_club
#: model_terms:ir.ui.view,arch_db:team_sports_club.welcome_article_body
msgid ""
"For annual contributions, you can easily manage specific prices for each "
"team by setting up pricelists. Once this is set up in the Teams app, you can "
"select all the players to whom you want to send the contribution request. A "
"smart button, <em>Request Contribution</em>, will appear. Click it to select "
"the correct product, assign a tag corresponding to the period, and generate "
"all the Sales Orders."
msgstr ""
"对于年度会费，您可以通过设置价目表，轻松管理各球队的特定价格。在“团队”应用中"
"完成此设置后，您可选择所有需要发送缴费通知的球员。此时将出现一个<em>请求缴费"
"</em>的智能按钮。点击它，选择正确的产品，分配一个对应缴费周期的标签，即可批量"
"生成所有销售订单。"

